            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">作者肯定隐瞒了很多事实，不过他揭露敌人的分析倒是非常可以一看。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1206859882">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1206859882" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1206859882" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1206859882">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/54957157/">猫吉里吉</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2017-06-24</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">末代皇帝溥仪的外国老师眼中的清王朝和皇室的最后时光。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1199825999">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1199825999" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1199825999" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1199825999">有用</a>
